# GrowEasy Environment Variables Setup
#
# This project has environment variables configured separately for the backend and frontend:
#
# 1. Backend: Copy './backend/.env.example' to './backend/.env' and configure:
#    - PORT: Port the backend server runs on
#    - CORS_ORIGIN: Allowed CORS origins
#    - GROQ_API_KEY: Your Groq API key (for Llama 3.3 70B)
#
# 2. Frontend: Copy './frontend/.env.example' to './frontend/.env' (or '.env.local') and configure:
#    - NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL: The URL of the backend API
